reviewText: One of the greatest CDs I've ever heard Thank You
This Cd has been a blessing to me.

Hard-driving, soul-stirring music and vocals. This is truly anointed music. Nancy is at her best in the title song and Jimmy Swaggart in the background makes it all come together perfectly. It doesn't get much better than this in Gospel Music. The title song alone would make it worth the cost.
My Mom just loves!  Amazing.  Item like described.
A friend saw this lady perform on TV and loved her.  She asked me to order the cd/dvd for her.  It's just what she expected.
